item.title: oh yea
item.description: hehe. I saw the pixies again on monday. and then again last night. I am retarded. they are getting harder as the nights progress. I wonder what tonight will bring. for me: naps. that is goddamned right. I am so tired. so so so tired. I am supposed to hang out. but oh no. I am going to nap. i got an interesting shout out on tank boys blog. heh. w00t.
